@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.62 - v1 + 0.38) + v0) + ((tmp + 0.54 - tmp + 0.44) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.06)))
    v2 = 0.98
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.21) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.45)))
    v1 = (tmp * (0.88 + 0.54))
    tmp = (0.04 + ((v1 + 0.80 / v2 + 0.43) / (tmp + 0.09 + v0 + 0.04)))
    data[tid] = v0
